OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780233071
OL,3,CTrains run again on main line where
OL,4,Cvital upgrades have been completed
OL,6,FTrains are running again through to
OL,7,FPortsmouth Harbour where Network Rail
OL,8,Fand South Western Railway have
OL,9,Fcompleted their latest phase of
OL,10,Fupgrades on the Portsmouth Direct Line.
OL,12,FOver the past five days, engineers
OL,13,Fhave been improving the resilience of
OL,14,Fthe infrastructure on the south coast
OL,15,Fwhile also progressing the next stage
OL,16,Fof the Havant re-signalling programme.
OL,18,FThis began in March and involves the
OL,19,Freplacement of ageing equipment that
OL,20,Fis becoming increasingly unreliable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
