PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780233071
OL,3,CTrains run again on main line where
OL,4,Cvital upgrades have been completed
OL,6,FOver the past year, signalling
OL,7,Ffailures have caused more than 18,500
OL,8,Fminutes of delays on the line.
OL,10,FThe Havant programme will see an
OL,11,Fadditional #120 million invested in
OL,12,Fthe Portsmouth Direct Line, on top of
OL,13,Fthe #129 million Farncombe to
OL,14,FPetersfield resignalling programme.
OL,16,FWhen completed in 2028, signalling
OL,17,Fwill transfer from the Havant Area
OL,18,FSignalling Centre to the Basingstoke
OL,19,FRail Operating Centre.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
