PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780233071
OL,3,CTrains run again on main line where
OL,4,Cvital upgrades have been completed
OL,6,FEngineers will return in October 2026
OL,7,Fand February 2027 to continue their
OL,8,Fwork.
OL,10,FDuring the five day closure, they
OL,11,Fcarried out a range of improvements,
OL,12,Fincluding:
OL,14,FIn total, engineers carried out around
OL,15,F1,660 hours of work during the
OL,16,Fclosure. When complete, passengers
OL,17,Fwill benefit from smoother, more
OL,18,Freliable journeys.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
