PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780233071
OL,3,CTrains run again on main line where
OL,4,Cvital upgrades have been completed
OL,6,FTom McNamee, Infrastructure Director
OL,7,Fsaid, "over the May half-term, we have
OL,8,Fcontinued to modernise signalling on
OL,9,Fthe Portsmouth Direct Line, replacing
OL,10,Fageing equipment in the Havant area
OL,11,Fthat is increasingly prone to failure
OL,12,Fand can cause delays for passengers.
OL,14,FWe've renewed key components on
OL,15,FPortcreek viaduct, where ageing wheel
OL,16,Ftimbers needed to be replaced to
OL,17,Fprevent further unplanned closures.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
